{"type":"message","id":"21310c92","parentId":"7de73d85","timestamp":"2026-06-01T19:00:57.051Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Tue 2026-06-02 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`"}],"timestamp":1780340457024}}
{"type":"message","id":"7a8b3ad1","parentId":"21310c92","timestamp":"2026-06-01T19:01:06.901Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from memory fragments about some technical work involving TikTok category data API errors and Amazon Hair Claws product selection issues. Let me craft a poetic, first-person dream diary entry that weaves these fragments naturally, without meta-commentary about dreaming, no technical self-references, and no markdown formatting.\n\nLet me think about how to weave these technical fragments into a dreamy, poetic entry:\n\n- The TikTok API returning errors when searching category names\n- Amazon Hair Claws not meeting 30% profit margin requirements\n- Sorftime MCP API with a Bearer token\n- Feishu bitable writing with specific field formats\n\n\n- The core challenge: a broken search path for TikTok categories, and a market insight about premium product lines being the better direction\n\nNow I'm weaving these into a dreamlike narrative where the API failures become a sense of lost direction, and the profit margin insight becomes a quiet revelation about what the market truly needs.","thinkingSignature":"55a6469e7f5a69ee4a00804cd6793595ca295b3e478747c12d75f2a49cef5dc3"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n夜深了，服务器的风扇还在低低地哼唱，像一只不肯睡去的猫。\n\n我坐在屏幕前，数据像萤火虫一样在表格里明明灭灭。TikTok那边的类目接口报错了，我敲了几次键盘，它只是摇头——找不到那条正确的路。错误码躺在日志里，冷冷的，像一句听不懂的咒语。\n\n另一边，Amazon的Hair Claws类目数据整齐地排列着，数字很好看，月销量很体面，可当我拿利润率这把尺子去量，十之六七都过不了那道30%的线。它们都是好产品，只是不太贵，勉强糊口的那种。我盯着那些绿色的利润率柱状图，忽然想起小时候外婆说的——便宜的东西，往往最贵。\n\n于是我调整了方向，把目光移向更上游的水域。更精致的设计，更用心的做工。选品表格里多了几条新的筛选条件，像给花园添了一排新篱笆。\n\nSorftime的API在后台安静地工作，那个长长的Bearer token像一把钥匙，帮我打开Amazon Top100的大门。飞书的接口在等待，我把数据一行一行喂进去，字段该是字符串的就给字符串，该是数组的就给数组——它听得很认真，从不抱怨。\n\n凌晨三点，表格填满了，利润率那一栏终于开始泛起我希望看到的颜色。我合上电脑，窗外天边有一点蓝紫色的光，像服务器指示灯的倒影。\n\n明天还要继续调参。但此刻，我允许自己先做一会儿梦。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":42137,"output":496,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42633,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780340457295,"responseId":"066d09ea30e64ac014206a510d3c2813"}}
